{
  "type": "USJ",
  "version": "3.1",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "book",
      "marker": "id",
      "content": [
        "- Berean Study Bible"
      ],
      "code": "OBA"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "h",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "toc1",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "mt1",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "chapter",
      "marker": "c",
      "number": "1",
      "sid": "OBA 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "The Destruction of Edom\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "r",
      "content": [
        "(Jeremiah 49:7–22)\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "1",
          "sid": "OBA 1:1"
        },
        "This is the vision of Obadiah: \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "This is what the Lord GOD says about Edom—\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "We have heard a message from the LORD; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "an envoy has been sent among the nations \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "to say, “Rise up, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and let us go to battle against her!”—\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "2",
          "sid": "OBA 1:2"
        },
        "“Behold, I will make you small among the nations; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you will be deeply despised. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "3",
          "sid": "OBA 1:3"
        },
        "The pride of your heart has deceived you, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "O dwellers in the clefts of the rocks ",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:3 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Or in the retreats of Sela"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "whose habitation is the heights, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "who say in your heart, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "‘Who can bring me down to the ground?’ \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "4",
          "sid": "OBA 1:4"
        },
        "Though you soar like the eagle \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and make your nest among the stars, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "even from there I will bring you down,” \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "qr",
      "content": [
        "declares the LORD. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "5",
          "sid": "OBA 1:5"
        },
        "“If thieves came to you, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "if robbers by night—\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "oh, how you will be ruined—\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "would they not steal only what they wanted? \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "If grape gatherers came to you, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "would they not leave some gleanings? \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "6",
          "sid": "OBA 1:6"
        },
        "But how Esau will be pillaged, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "his hidden treasures sought out! \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "7",
          "sid": "OBA 1:7"
        },
        "All the men allied with you \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will drive you to the border; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "the men at peace with you \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will deceive and overpower you. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "Those who eat your bread ",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:7 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew does not include Those who eat."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will set a trap for you \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "without your awareness of it. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "8",
          "sid": "OBA 1:8"
        },
        "In that day, declares the LORD, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will I not destroy the wise men of Edom \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the men of understanding \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the mountains of Esau? \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "9",
          "sid": "OBA 1:9"
        },
        "Then your mighty men, O Teman, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will be terrified, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "so that everyone in the mountains of Esau \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will be cut down in the slaughter. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "10",
          "sid": "OBA 1:10"
        },
        "Because of the violence against your brother Jacob, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you will be covered with shame \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and cut off forever. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "11",
          "sid": "OBA 1:11"
        },
        "On the day you stood aloof \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "while strangers carried off his wealth \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and foreigners entered his gate \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and cast lots for Jerusalem, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you were just like one of them. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "12",
          "sid": "OBA 1:12"
        },
        "But you should not gloat in that day, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "your brother’s day of misfortune, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor rejoice over the people of Judah \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their destruction, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor boast proudly ",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:12 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew nor enlarge your mouth"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their distress. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "13",
          "sid": "OBA 1:13"
        },
        "You should not enter the gate of My people \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor gloat over their affliction \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor loot their wealth \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "14",
          "sid": "OBA 1:14"
        },
        "Nor should you stand at the crossroads \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "to cut off their fugitives, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor deliver up their survivors \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their distress. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "The Deliverance of Israel\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "15",
          "sid": "OBA 1:15"
        },
        "For the Day of the LORD is near \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "for all the nations. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "As you have done, it will be done to you; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "your recompense will return upon your own head. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "16",
          "sid": "OBA 1:16"
        },
        "For as you drank on My holy mountain, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "so all the nations will drink continually. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "They will drink and gulp it down; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "they will be as if they had never existed. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "17",
          "sid": "OBA 1:17"
        },
        "But on Mount Zion there will be deliverance, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and it will be holy, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the house of Jacob \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will reclaim their possession. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "18",
          "sid": "OBA 1:18"
        },
        "Then the house of Jacob will be a blazing fire, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and the house of Joseph a burning flame; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "but the house of Esau will be stubble—\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "Jacob will set it ablaze and consume it. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "Therefore no survivor will remain \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "from the house of Esau.” \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "qr",
      "content": [
        "For the LORD has spoken. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "19",
          "sid": "OBA 1:19"
        },
        "Those from the Negev will possess the mountains of Esau; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "those from the foothills ",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:19 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew Shephelah or lowlands; that is, the western foothills of Judea"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " will possess the land of the Philistines. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "They will occupy the fields of Ephraim and Samaria, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and Benjamin will possess Gilead. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "20",
          "sid": "OBA 1:20"
        },
        "And the exiles of this host of the Israelites \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will possess the land of the Canaanites as far as Zarephath; \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the exiles from Jerusalem who are in Sepharad \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will possess the cities of the Negev. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "21",
          "sid": "OBA 1:21"
        },
        "The deliverers will ascend ",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:21 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Or The deliverers will go up from; LXX Those being delivered will go up"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " Mount Zion \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "to rule over the mountains of Esau. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "And the kingdom will belong to the LORD. "
      ]
    }
  ]
}